stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_init: matrix = []
    q_init --> q_iter_blob: for blob_index, blob in enumerate(blobs)
    q_iter_blob --> q_compute_cells: has next blob
    q_iter_blob --> q_return: no more blobs
    q_compute_cells --> q_iter_cell: cells, proofs = compute_cells_and_kzg_proofs(blob)
    q_iter_cell --> q_append: has next cell
    q_iter_cell --> q_iter_blob: no more cells
    q_append --> q_iter_cell: matrix.append(MatrixEntry(cell, proof, cell_index, blob_index))
    q_return --> [*]: return matrix
